	private void btnSearch_M_Click(object sender, System.EventArgs args)
	{
		// ** Place Event Handling Code Here **
		//string Site = cbSite.Text;
		//string PartNum = txtInvNum.Text;
		string GroupID = "";
		if (edvGroup.CurrentDataRow!= null) 
		{
		    GroupID = edvGroup.CurrentDataRow["GroupID"].ToString();
		}
		
		
		//string ToDate = dateTo.DateTime.ToString("yyyyMMdd");
		string sql = "[E3S_PROD_CostPart] '"+oCon.CompanyID+"','"+GroupID+"','M'"; //1 select raw data
		DataSet ds1 = oCon.ExecuteQuery(sql);
		DataTable tb = ds1.Tables[0];
		
				
		
		grdManuPart.DataSource = tb;
		grdManuPart.ExFormatGrid(false,false,true,true,false,true,true,true, true,true);



		if (grdManuPart.DisplayLayout.Bands.Count > 0)
			{
				foreach (UltraGridColumn col in grdManuPart.DisplayLayout.Bands[0].Columns)
				{
					col.CellActivation = Activation.ActivateOnly;
					if(col.DataType == typeof(decimal))
					{
						col.MaskInput = "-n,nnn.nnnnn";
						col.Format = "#,##0.00000";
					}
				}
			}

	
//		foreach(UltraGridColumn col in grdManuPart.DisplayLayout.Bands[0].Columns)
//		{
//			col.CellActivation = Activation.ActivateOnly;
//		}
		
	}
